OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772223642
OL,3,CMother of murdered toddler
OL,4,C'devastated' after son's grave
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,FThe mother of murdered toddler James
OL,8,FBulger says she is "devastated" after
OL,9,Fher son's grave was targeted in a
OL,10,F"truly shocking" act of vandalism.
OL,12,FOfficers were called to Kirkdale
OL,13,FCemetery, in Liverpool, at
OL,14,Fapproximately 4.20pm on Thursday, 26
OL,15,FFebruary, following reports that the
OL,16,Fmemorial to the murdered toddler had
OL,17,Fbeen significantly damaged and items
OL,18,Fstolen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
