PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772223642
OL,3,CMother of murdered toddler
OL,4,C'devastated' after son's grave
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,FMerseyside Police say the site was
OL,8,Ftargeted during the day, with two
OL,9,Flarge marble angels positioned on
OL,10,Feither side of the headstone damaged.
OL,12,FA smaller angel statue was discovered
OL,13,Fafter being discarded in a nearby bin
OL,14,Fand a yellow teddy bear, left as a
OL,15,Ftribute, was stolen from the site.
OL,17,FPolice believe the incident took place
OL,18,Fbetween 9.00am and 3.00pm, while the
OL,19,Fcemetery was open to the public.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
