PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772223642
OL,3,CMother of murdered toddler
OL,4,C'devastated' after son's grave
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,F"Today I felt my heart break once
OL,8,Fagain," James' mum Denise Fergus said
OL,9,Fin a statement on social media as she
OL,10,Furgently appealed for help to find the
OL,11,Fperpetrator.
OL,13,FShe added: "I'm devastated someone
OL,14,Fcould be so cruel and hurtful to my
OL,15,FJames."
OL,17,FMerseyside Police inspector Chris
OL,18,FTaylor condemned the act, stating that
OL,19,Fthe force is "determined" to find
OL,20,Fthose responsible for the damage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
