PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772223642
OL,3,CMother of murdered toddler
OL,4,C'devastated' after son's grave
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,F"To vandalise a grave is completely
OL,8,Fabhorrent and it's truly shocking to
OL,9,Fthink that someone could commit such
OL,10,Fan appalling act," he said.
OL,12,FDetectives are now reviewing CCTV
OL,13,Ffootage and are seeking witnesses who
OL,14,Fmay have been visiting the cemetery
OL,15,Fduring the six-hour window.
OL,17,FInspector Taylor added: "If you were
OL,18,Fin the area and saw anything
OL,19,Fsuspicious or have any information
OL,20,Fabout what happened, please get in
OL,21,Ftouch as a matter of urgency."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
