OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772223642
OL,3,CMother of murdered toddler
OL,4,C'devastated' after son's grave
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,FJames was two-year-old when he was
OL,8,Fabducted from shopping centre in
OL,9,FBootle and murdered by two 10-year-old
OL,10,Fboys in 1993.
OL,12,FRobert Thompson and Jon Venables
OL,13,Fwalked James over two miles to a
OL,14,Frailway line, where they tortured and
OL,15,Fkilled him, which sparked a national-
OL,16,Fwide debate on the age of criminal
OL,17,Fresponsibility.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
